high_descs: Turn left and go to the bath tub on the other side.
Pick up and pink bar soap in the bath tub.
Turn right and go to the sink.
Wash the pink bar soap in the sink with running water.
Turn left and go back to the bath tub.
Place the soap in the bath tub.
anns.task_desc: Put the washed soap in the bath tub.

high_descs: turn left and move to he bath tub
pick up the soap from the tub
turn right and head to the sink
place the soap in the sink and wet it
turn around and head to the tub
place the soap in the tub
anns.task_desc: place a wet soap in the tub

high_descs: Turn left and face the tub in front of you.
Take the soap from the tub in front of you.
Turn right then face the sink to your left.
Clean the soap in the sink in front of you and take it out.
Turn around, turn right, then face the tub on your right.
Place the soap in the tub in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place clean soap in the tub.
